Class EndGameResponse

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsoftware.ll13.network.response.Response
it.polimi.ingsoftware.ll13.network.response.adventure.EndGameResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class EndGameResponse extends Response
Represents a response indicating the end of a game. It contains information about the players' names and their respective points at the conclusion of the game. This response is typically sent by the server to the clients to convey the final standings. This class extends the Response class and implements functionality to process this specific type of response using the provided Handler.
